parameters: Voices could be heard from somewhere.

Iwao: "Why didn't you go through with it? You could have easily taken
down two women."

Takeru: "That woman from before... I feel like I've seen her
somewhere..."
Takeru: "Besides, that woman seemed to notice my presence..."
Iwao: "So you were being cautious."

Takeru: "Yes, she's not an ordinary woman. It would be troublesome if
one got away, so I let them be."

Iwao: "Good job, that was the right decision. You saved your own
life."
Takeru: "Eh? What do you mean by that...?"
Iwao: "Don't you get it?"

Iwao: "If you were foolish enough to attack a pair, I would have had
to eliminate you."
Iwao: "The thing I hate the most is risk."
Iwao: "Why do you think I would come to a risky scene like this?"
Takeru: "...I'm sorry. I don't understand."

Iwao: "I'm here taking risks not just to check out the women. It's to
monitor your actions."

Iwao: "It's so I can deal with it appropriately if you get caught in
some police sting operation."
Iwao: "The police seem desperate to gather evidence to catch me."
Takeru: "Please rest assured. I won't make such a mistake..."

Iwao: "I hope that's true... That woman from before will likely show
up here again. There's something about her. My instincts are telling
me so."
Takeru: "That's not good. Should we retreat then?"

Iwao: "Normally, retreating would be the smart move, but she's an
exceptional catch. She's worth the risk."
Iwao: "Even if she turns out to be a cop..."
Takeru: "Even if she's with the police?"

Iwao: "Don't forget the favor I did for you at Agas. Without my
information, you'd be behind bars right now."

Takeru: "...I understand. I'm nothing but grateful to you, Iwao-san.
I'll take this job seriously."
Iwao: "Come over here for a second."

Iwao: "I'll hide out here. It's to prepare for the off chance that you
get caught."
Takeru: "Iwao-san... that place is..."
Iwao: "What is it?"
Takeru: "That spot is... heh. It made me laugh."
Takeru: "Given the situation, heh heh heh."
Iwao: "You... do you have a death wish...?"

Takeru: "Sorry... It's just that you have such a cool face, yet you
actually have a sense of humor."
Iwao: "All of this is for the sake of the job."
Yui: (Iwao Chikunai... so he was here after all.)

Yui: (It seems like they've caught on to my strategy, but this is the
perfect chance to catch them.)
Yui: (If they're up for it, then I'm going all in too. Just you wait!)
